snippet.title: Heaven is for Real - Hannity interview

localized.description: Colton Burpo, who had a near-death experience on an operating bed, tells Sean Hannity of his experiences in heaven. His dad Todd and Randall Wallace, director of the movie Heaven is For Real are also interviewed. Sean asks Colton if everyone goes to heaven. He responds, "Only those who love Jesus."
